This is the Google App Engine app that runs on https://wpsnitch.appspot.com/

If you want to create your own app or service to retrieve this information,
read the code and replicate its behaviour--please, don't use the appspot
website as an API! It's on the free tier of App Engine and its quota is very
limited.

Please don't ask me if you can create an app based on this code. Yes, you can.

Everything is in the public domain, do whatever you want with the code.
